using namespace std;

int main()
{
    int noc;
    cin>>noc;

    for (int i = 0; i < noc; i++) {

	int x11,y11,x12,y12,x21,y21,x22,y22;

	cin>>x11>>y11>>x12>>y12;
	cin>>x21>>y21>>x22>>y22;

	if (x21 > x11 && x21 < x12) {

	    if (y21 > y11 && y21 < y12) {

		cout<<x21<<" "<<y21<<" ";
		if (x12 < x22) cout<<x12<<" "; else cout<<x22<<" ";
		if (y12 < y22) cout<<y12<<endl; else cout<<y22<<endl;

	    } else if(y22 > y11 && y22 < y12) {

		cout<<x21<<" ";
		if (y11 > y21) cout<<y11<<" "; else cout<<y21<<" ";
		if (x12 < x22) cout<<x12<<" "; else cout<<x22<<" ";
		cout<<y22<<endl;

	    } else

		cout<<"No Overlap\n";

	} else if (x22 > x11 && x22 < x12) {

	    if (y21 > y11 && y21 < y12) {

		if (x11 > x21) cout<<x11<<" "; else cout<<x21<<" ";
		cout<<y21<<" "<<x22<<" ";
		if (y12 < y22) cout<<y12<<endl; else cout<<y22<<endl;

	    } else if(y22 > y11 && y22 < y12) {

		if (x11 < x21) cout<<x11<<" "; else cout<<x21<<" ";
		if (y11 > y21) cout<<y11<<" "; else cout<<y21<<" ";
		cout<<x22<<" "<<y22<<endl;

	    } else

		cout<<"No Overlap\n";

	} else

	    cout<<"No Overlap\n";
    }

    return(0);
}
